the nature and history of the proceeding 1 the dispute at the heart of this proceeding is about the correct calculation of the rate of pay for a part-time employee entitled to long service leave.
a collective agreement between the parties to the proceeding incorporates by reference legislative provisions governing entitlements to long service leave in victoria.
